you can easly create them with ctrl + t

then if you want to add new rows go to the last cell at the Right
and press TAB

to delete the table structure (but not the data) go to
'Table Design' and click on 'Convert to range'

on the 'Design' tab you will have more settings available

'Banded rows' will allow you to have more readability

'Total row' will provide some 'sum'
